data.description: This alluring Cape Cod home offers a generous 2,000+ square feet of living space, featuring four bedrooms and two bathrooms thoughtfully distributed between the main and upper levels. The heart of the home is a spacious great room with vaulted ceilings, creating an inviting atmosphere for relaxation and gatherings, while the adjacent dining area provides ample space for family dinners and entertaining. Both bathrooms newly remodeled. A basement studio setup for recording, and the garage under the home ensures convenient vehicle storage. The classic Cape Cod design and timeless charm make this property an inviting place to call home, providing the perfect balance of space and character for comfortable living. UHP home warranty included.
